Interface Relationship

All Known Implementing Classes:
RelationshipImpl
public interface Relationship

A representation of the model object 'Relationship'.

The following features are supported:

  • Key Pair
  • Config
  • Foreign Key Table
  • Many
  • Name
  • Primary Key Table
